Class NetworkService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.NetworkService

  • public final class NetworkService
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides access to a network level functionality.
    提供对网络级功能的访问。

      CertificateVerifier getCertificateVerifier()
      Returns currently registered SSL certificate verifier or null if no custom SSL certificate verifier is currently registered.
      返回当前注册的SSL证书验证程序；如果当前未注册自定义SSL证书验证程序，则返回null。

      Returns NetworkDelegate associated with the current BrowserContext instance.

    • Method Detail

      • getNetworkDelegate

        public NetworkDelegate getNetworkDelegate()
        Returns NetworkDelegate associated with the current BrowserContext instance. By default this method returns null.
        返回与当前BrowserContext实例关联的NetworkDelegate。默认情况下，此方法返回null。
        Returns:
        the NetworkDelegate associated with this Browser instance or null if there's no registered NetworkDelegate. 与此浏览器实例相关联的，如果尚未注册。

      • setNetworkDelegate

        public void setNetworkDelegate(NetworkDelegate delegate)
        Configures the current Browser instance to use new HTTP request/response handler to process all HTTP requests/responses. The NetworkDelegate can be used for intercepting HTTP request/response headers and modifying them on the fly.

        To reset NetworkDelegate and enable default behavior, pass null to this method.
        将当前浏览器实例配置为使用新的HTTP请求/响应处理程序来处理所有HTTP请求/响应。 NetworkDelegate可用于拦截HTTP请求/响应标头并即时对其进行修改。若要重置NetworkDelegate并启用默认行为，请将null传递给此方法。
        Parameters:
        delegate - the new NetworkDelegate handler. -新的处理程序。

      • getCertificateVerifier

        public CertificateVerifier getCertificateVerifier()
        Returns currently registered SSL certificate verifier or null if no custom SSL certificate verifier is currently registered. By default this method returns null, so Chromium default verifier is used.
        返回当前注册的SSL证书验证程序；如果当前未注册自定义SSL证书验证程序，则返回null。默认情况下，此方法返回null，因此使用Chromium默认验证程序。
        Returns:
        the registered SSL certificate verifier or null if no custom SSL certificate verifier is currently registered. 已注册的SSL证书验证程序，或者当前未注册任何自定义SSL证书验证程序。
        Since:
        6.3

      • setCertificateVerifier

        public void setCertificateVerifier(CertificateVerifier verifier)
        Sets custom SSL certificate verifier. Pass null to reset custom SSL certificate verifier and switch on default Chromium verifier.
        设置自定义SSL证书验证程序。传递null以重置自定义SSL证书验证程序并打开默认的Chromium验证程序。
        Parameters:
        verifier - SSL certificate verifier. Can be null. -SSL证书验证程序。可 。
        Since:
        6.3

      • getResourceHandler

        public ResourceHandler getResourceHandler()
        Returns registered resource handler or null if no resource handler is currently registered. By default this method returns null, so all resources will be downloaded from a web server as well.
        返回已注册的资源处理程序；如果当前未注册任何资源处理程序，则返回null。默认情况下，此方法返回null，因此所有资源也将从Web服务器下载。
        Returns:
        the registered resource handler or null if no resource handler is currently registered. 已注册的资源处理程序，或者当前未注册任何资源处理程序。

      • setResourceHandler

        public void setResourceHandler(ResourceHandler handler)
        Sets resource handler that will be invoked every time to ask whether specified resource (HTML, image, JavaScript, CSS file, etc.) should be downloaded from a web server or not.
        设置将每次调用以询问是否应从Web服务器下载指定资源（HTML，图像，JavaScript，CSS文件等）的资源处理程序。
        Parameters:
        handler - a new resource handler. Can be null. -一个新的资源处理程序。可 。

      • getServerWhiteList

        public java.lang.String getServerWhiteList()
        Returns a string that represents comma/semicolon separated server HTTP authorization white list of server URLs.
        返回一个字符串，该字符串表示服务器URL的逗号/分号分隔的服务器HTTP授权白名单。
        Returns:
        a string that represents comma/semicolon separated server HTTP authorization white list of server URLs. 一个字符串，代表用逗号/分号分隔的服务器URL服务器HTTP授权白名单。
        Since:
        6.8

      • setServerWhiteList

        public void setServerWhiteList(java.lang.String serverWhiteList)
        Modifies server HTTP authorization white list with the given serverWhiteList URLs. By default, server white list is empty.
        使用给定的serverWhiteList URL修改服务器HTTP授权白名单。默认情况下，服务器白名单为空。
        Parameters:
        serverWhiteList - comma/semicolon separated server HTTP authorization white list of server URLs. For example: "*example.com,*foobar.com,*baz" -逗号/分号分隔的服务器URL服务器HTTP授权白名单。例如：“ * example.com，* foobar.com，* baz”
        Since:
        6.8

        Returns:
        a string that represents comma/semicolon separated HTTP network delegate authorization white list of server URLs. 一个字符串，代表服务器URL的逗号/分号分隔的HTTP网络委托授权白名单。
        Since:
        6.8

      • setDelegateWhiteList

        public void setDelegateWhiteList(java.lang.String delegateWhiteList)
        Modifies HTTP network delegate white list with the given delegateWhiteList URLs. By default, network delegate white list is empty.
        使用给定的委托WhiteList URL修改HTTP网络委托白名单。默认情况下，网络委托白名单为空。
        Parameters:
        delegateWhiteList - comma/semicolon separated authorization white list of network delegate URLs. For example: "*example.com,*foobar.com,*baz" -以逗号/分号分隔的网络委托URL授权白名单。例如：“ * example.com，* foobar.com，* baz”
        Since:
        6.8
